      "description": "Offered for sale is a mechanically sorted BMW E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure VANOS. Power is managed through a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and a Variable M Differential Lock, ensuring linear torque delivery and exceptional rear-end bite. The chassis has been enhanced with a reinforced rear subframe and polyurethane bushings to address factory fatigue points, while the suspension features Bilstein B16 coilovers for sharpened damping and roll center correction. Recent technical maintenance includes a comprehensive valve clearance adjustment and a cooling system refresh with an aluminum radiator. This is a performance-first example with a robust drivetrain, perfect for the purist seeking a visceral driving experience.",
